    <detaileddescription>
<sect1 id="structs_page_1structs_intro">
<title>Introduction</title>
<para>The structs module contains fundamental data structures used throughout the AnalysisG framework. These structures define configuration options, data containers, and type definitions.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="structs_page_1structs_settings">
<title>Settings Structure</title>
<para>The <computeroutput><ref refid="structsettings__t" kindref="compound">settings_t</ref></computeroutput> structure configures analysis behavior:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">struct<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structsettings__t" kindref="compound">settings_t</ref><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::string<sp/>output;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Output<sp/>directory<sp/>path</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structsettings__t_1a383cb4d94ff68571dc4cd2e8a9f4d00f" kindref="member">threads</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Number<sp/>of<sp/>processing<sp/>threads</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structsettings__t_1a574cb98d49f69c527eed1fe1c64e22a5" kindref="member">batch_size</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Default<sp/>batch<sp/>size</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">bool</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>cache_events;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Enable<sp/>event<sp/>caching</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">bool</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>cache_graphs;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Enable<sp/>graph<sp/>caching</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>...<sp/>additional<sp/>settings</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="structs_page_1structs_optimizer">
<title>Optimizer Parameters</title>
<para>The <computeroutput><ref refid="structoptimizer__params__t" kindref="compound">optimizer_params_t</ref></computeroutput> structure configures model training:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">struct<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structoptimizer__params__t" kindref="compound">optimizer_params_t</ref><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">double</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>learning_rate;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Initial<sp/>learning<sp/>rate</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>epochs;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Number<sp/>of<sp/>training<sp/>epochs</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>batch_size;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Training<sp/>batch<sp/>size</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::string<sp/><ref refid="structoptimizer__params__t_1adcdb256ae898edeae6b51c14d7fb711b" kindref="member">optimizer</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Optimizer<sp/>type<sp/>(Adam,<sp/>SGD,<sp/>etc.)</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>k_folds;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Number<sp/>of<sp/>cross-validation<sp/>folds</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">bool</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>early_stopping;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Enable<sp/>early<sp/>stopping</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>patience;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Epochs<sp/>before<sp/>early<sp/>stopping</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>...<sp/>additional<sp/>parameters</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="structs_page_1structs_graph">
<title>Graph Data Structure</title>
<para>The <computeroutput><ref refid="structgraph__t" kindref="compound">graph_t</ref></computeroutput> structure represents a processed graph:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">struct<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structgraph__t" kindref="compound">graph_t</ref><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structgraph__t_1a45783311aac5e6f50f23246f0cf407d1" kindref="member">num_nodes</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Number<sp/>of<sp/>nodes<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>graph</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">long</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structgraph__t_1af5c8af15275269308e0ed7876ddb7979" kindref="member">event_index</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Source<sp/>event<sp/>index</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">double</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structgraph__t_1a07320e7cdf65b625be449ac9ca4515a6" kindref="member">event_weight</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Event<sp/>weight<sp/>for<sp/>normalization</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">bool</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structgraph__t_1ac2b2cef7e657d1d2e7e80ee0a4505a56" kindref="member">preselection</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Whether<sp/>graph<sp/>passed<sp/>preselection</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Feature<sp/>access<sp/>methods</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>torch::Tensor*<sp/><ref refid="structgraph__t_1ae55e7c4ea7a4563757d939a96afb52a3" kindref="member">get_data_node</ref>(std::string<sp/><ref refid="namespacename" kindref="compound">name</ref>,<sp/>model*);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>torch::Tensor*<sp/><ref refid="structgraph__t_1acfe6c582dfe47bafa5cde3f4d87059a0" kindref="member">get_truth_node</ref>(std::string<sp/><ref refid="namespacename" kindref="compound">name</ref>,<sp/>model*);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>torch::Tensor*<sp/><ref refid="structgraph__t_1abaf966dadf0b69eedee0b7b3ca12f35f" kindref="member">get_data_edge</ref>(std::string<sp/><ref refid="namespacename" kindref="compound">name</ref>,<sp/>model*);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>torch::Tensor*<sp/><ref refid="structgraph__t_1af1b623e3198464189dbab71222c3f3ac" kindref="member">get_truth_edge</ref>(std::string<sp/><ref refid="namespacename" kindref="compound">name</ref>,<sp/>model*);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>torch::Tensor*<sp/><ref refid="structgraph__t_1aff4d59b1f531a9c2a52db5b6031786a4" kindref="member">get_data_graph</ref>(std::string<sp/><ref refid="namespacename" kindref="compound">name</ref>,<sp/>model*);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>torch::Tensor*<sp/><ref refid="structgraph__t_1abb0d4875f7295f1db37a97f6671a6a52" kindref="member">get_truth_graph</ref>(std::string<sp/><ref refid="namespacename" kindref="compound">name</ref>,<sp/>model*);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>torch::Tensor*<sp/><ref refid="structgraph__t_1abac5c01cde57a746f44b24eac9a34fa0" kindref="member">get_edge_index</ref>(model*);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>...</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="structs_page_1structs_event">
<title>Event Data Structure</title>
<para>The <computeroutput><ref refid="structevent__t" kindref="compound">event_t</ref></computeroutput> structure contains raw event data:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">struct<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structevent__t" kindref="compound">event_t</ref><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">long</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structevent__t_1a64d57a05a578b1fb8990a73c1116bc4c" kindref="member">index</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Event<sp/>index</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">double</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structevent__t_1a4d9b9926d247fe1b0392ce01f59ae459" kindref="member">weight</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Event<sp/>weight</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::string<sp/><ref refid="structevent__t_1a313f1f055a86fd413dbd14f2dbfa6ed9" kindref="member">tree</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Source<sp/>TTree<sp/>name</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::string<sp/><ref refid="structevent__t_1a34c3a0cdf480b7dff4144989d80a53d9" kindref="member">hash</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Event<sp/>hash<sp/>for<sp/>identification</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>...</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="structs_page_1structs_folds">
<title>Cross-Validation Folds</title>
<para>The <computeroutput><ref refid="structfolds__t" kindref="compound">folds_t</ref></computeroutput> structure manages k-fold cross-validation:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">struct<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structfolds__t" kindref="compound">folds_t</ref><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structfolds__t_1abf8a14364fa18f04ba5d13e7d4b62556" kindref="member">k</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Current<sp/>fold<sp/>index</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::string<sp/><ref refid="structfolds__t_1a2f5c9cc76bcf002f95e4a67b3dcf2404" kindref="member">hash</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Fold<sp/>identifier</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::vector&lt;long&gt;<sp/>train;<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Training<sp/>indices</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::vector&lt;long&gt;<sp/>test;<sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Test<sp/>indices</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>...</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="structs_page_1structs_property_doc">
<title>Property System</title>
<para>The <computeroutput>cproperty</computeroutput> template provides a property system:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">template</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>&lt;</highlight><highlight class="keyword">typename</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>T,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">typename</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>O&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">class<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classcproperty" kindref="compound">cproperty</ref><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">public</highlight><highlight class="normal">:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="classcproperty_1a31b26b5ffb20bbf8d8ee38e0755a9819" kindref="member">set_getter</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>(*<ref refid="classcproperty_1a213f4d26d6254ff2e67a98c21b1f3212" kindref="member">getter</ref>)(T*,<sp/>O*));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="classcproperty_1af4583ba4cf4ebc53f870a2de8f110da7" kindref="member">set_setter</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>(*<ref refid="classcproperty_1a7be2b33f86b539371ae2db6611afe0ce" kindref="member">setter</ref>)(T*,<sp/>O*));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="classcproperty_1a41a70e8e01c9b1a20b94d2dbf1a6b214" kindref="member">set_object</ref>(O*<sp/><ref refid="classcproperty_1a58aa65f7de6c3eb5f41dabd9bd56bbb6" kindref="member">obj</ref>);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">operator</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>T();<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Implicit<sp/>conversion<sp/>(getter)</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><ref refid="classcproperty" kindref="compound">cproperty</ref>&amp;<sp/><ref refid="classcproperty_1a9709c338b860f7142dfeacd15e4f7426" kindref="member">operator=</ref>(T);<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Assignment<sp/>(setter)</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Usage example:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">class<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">MyClass<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">public</highlight><highlight class="normal">:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><ref refid="classcproperty" kindref="compound">cproperty&lt;int, MyClass&gt;</ref><sp/>value;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>MyClass()<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>value.<ref refid="classcproperty_1a31b26b5ffb20bbf8d8ee38e0755a9819" kindref="member">set_getter</ref>(get_value);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>value.<ref refid="classcproperty_1af4583ba4cf4ebc53f870a2de8f110da7" kindref="member">set_setter</ref>(set_value);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>value.<ref refid="classcproperty_1a41a70e8e01c9b1a20b94d2dbf1a6b214" kindref="member">set_object</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">this</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">private</highlight><highlight class="normal">:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>m_value;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">static</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>get_value(</highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal">*<sp/>out,<sp/>MyClass*<sp/>obj)<sp/>{<sp/>*out<sp/>=<sp/>obj-&gt;m_value;<sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">static</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>set_value(</highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal">*<sp/>in,<sp/>MyClass*<sp/>obj)<sp/>{<sp/>obj-&gt;m_value<sp/>=<sp/>*in;<sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="structs_page_1structs_enums">
